==================================== LAB - 4 ====================================

--> ChromaDB and Sentence Transformer
    -> Limitation of TF-IDF/BoW: Only matches exact keywords. Cannot understand "car" ~ "automobile".
    -> Solution: Vector Embeddings (Sentence Transformers)
        -> Converts text into list of numbers (vectors) representing *meaning*.
        -> "King" - "Man" + "Woman" ≈ "Queen"
    -> ChromaDB (Vector Database)
        -> Specialized database to store these vectors.
        -> Allows "Semantic Search": Finding nearest neighbors (most similar meaning) instead of just matching words.
        -> Fast retrieval for RAG (Retrieval Augmented Generation).

